Project: Med-Peptides
Module: Institutional & Clinical Inquiries page
Priority: High
Platform: Desktop first

Objective:
Implement and validate the inquiry form so that:
1. The “Schedule Video Call” action opens the correct booking page:
   https://us.bigin.online/org900319019/bookings/mhs
2. The booking-related email shown and used in contact workflows is:
   business@Med-Peptides.com
3. The selected value in “Identify your inquiry type” is reflected correctly in the form state and submission payload.
4. The form cannot be submitted unless all required fields are completed correctly.
5. Add a small validation test suite to confirm the form works.

Context:
Current page includes:
- Inquiry type selector with options such as Clinics, Pharmacies, Researchers, Distributors
- Institutional Inquiry form with fields:
  Full Name
  Email Address
  Phone Number
  Inquiry Type
  Message / Details
  Supporting Files (optional)
- “Schedule Video Call” CTA
- General contact area

Required implementation:

A. Booking CTA
- Wire the “Schedule Video Call” CTA to open:
  https://us.bigin.online/org900319019/bookings/mhs
- Open in a new tab.
- Track click event:
  booking_cta_clicked
- Store source metadata:
  page = institutional_inquiry
  region = current selected region
  inquiry_type = current selected inquiry type if available

B. Contact Email
- Replace any old booking/contact email for this section with:
  business@Med-Peptides.com
- Use this email consistently in:
  visible contact blocks
  fallback contact actions
  submission metadata if email routing is needed

C. Inquiry Type Reflection
- The selection in “Identify your inquiry type” must sync with the actual form field “Inquiry Type”.
- If user clicks:
  Clinics → Inquiry Type defaults to “Clinic Inquiry”
  Pharmacies → Inquiry Type defaults to “Pharmacy Inquiry”
  Researchers → Inquiry Type defaults to “Research Inquiry”
  Distributors → Inquiry Type defaults to “Distributor Inquiry”
- If user later changes the dropdown manually, keep the manual value and do not overwrite it unless they intentionally switch inquiry type again.
- Highlight the selected inquiry type button clearly.

D. Required Field Validation
Make these fields required:
- Full Name
- Email Address
- Phone Number
- Inquiry Type
- Message / Details

Validation rules:
- Full Name:
  minimum 2 words preferred
  minimum 3 characters
- Email Address:
  valid email format required
- Phone Number:
  must contain valid numeric content after country code
  minimum sensible length by international standards
- Inquiry Type:
  cannot be empty
- Message / Details:
  minimum 10 characters
  trim whitespace
- Supporting Files:
  optional

E. Submission Blocking
- Disable the submit button until required fields are valid.
- If user tries to submit with invalid data, show inline validation under each invalid field.
- Do not use browser-native ugly validation popups.
- Use clean inline error messages.

Suggested error copy:
- Full Name: “Please enter your full name.”
- Email Address: “Please enter a valid email address.”
- Phone Number: “Please enter a valid phone number.”
- Inquiry Type: “Please select an inquiry type.”
- Message / Details: “Please provide a short description of your request.”

F. UX Improvements
- If an inquiry type card is selected, mirror that state visibly in the form.
- Keep the selected card persistent while editing the form.
- Add success state after submit:
  “Your inquiry has been submitted successfully. Our team will contact you shortly.”
- Keep response expectation text:
  “Response within 24 hours (Business Days)”
- Ensure the WhatsApp indicator is only visual and does not break layout.

G. Submission Payload
On submit, send/store:
- full_name
- email
- country_code
- phone_number
- inquiry_type
- message
- supporting_files metadata if any
- source_page = institutional_inquiry
- selected_inquiry_card
- region
- timestamp
- user_id if logged in

H. Testing
Create a lightweight form test suite covering:
1. Clinics card selection updates Inquiry Type field correctly
2. Pharmacies card selection updates Inquiry Type field correctly
3. Researchers card selection updates Inquiry Type field correctly
4. Distributors card selection updates Inquiry Type field correctly
5. Submit button remains disabled when required fields are empty
6. Invalid email blocks submission
7. Empty message blocks submission
8. Valid form enables submission
9. Schedule Video Call opens the correct Bigin booking URL
10. business@Med-Peptides.com appears in the correct contact area

I. Manual QA checklist
Run these manual checks:
- Select each inquiry type card and verify form sync
- Enter invalid email and confirm inline error
- Leave message empty and confirm submission blocked
- Submit a valid inquiry and confirm success state
- Click “Schedule Video Call” and verify it opens:
  https://us.bigin.online/org900319019/bookings/mhs
- Confirm visible email is:
  business@Med-Peptides.com

J. Success criteria
- Inquiry type card and form field remain synchronized
- Required field validation works correctly
- Form cannot be submitted with incomplete required data
- Booking CTA opens the correct page
- business@Med-Peptides.com is used consistently
- No broken states, no silent submission failures, no browser-native validation popups